    {"key": "ui.danmaku.boundary.teach.amulet", "en": "FOLLOW THE GAPS, NOT THE CHARMS.", "ja": "札ではなく、隙間を追う。"},
    {"key": "ui.danmaku.boundary.teach.memory", "en": "THE OLD SAFE LANE MOVED ONE TILE.", "ja": "前の安全路は一マス動いた。"},
