    {"key": "ui.exploration.note.reimu", "en": "REIMU WATCHES THE CUP INSTEAD OF YOU.", "ja": "霊夢はこちらでなく湯呑みを見ている。"},
    {"key": "ui.exploration.note.tree", "en": "THE OLD TREE LEANS AWAY FROM THE BOUNDARY.", "ja": "古木は結界から離れるように傾いている。"},
    {"key": "ui.exploration.objective.complete", "en": "THE EMPTY PLACE HAS AN ANSWER.", "ja": "空いた場所の意味が見えた。"},
